title: Reform Jersey look for new members
text:
Jersey's only political party is trying to recruit new members.
A meeting held last night gave an opportunity for the public to discuss political issues.
It came after the States' decision to cut millions from the public sector.
Around 50 people attended.
The party say they are looking for an alternative to States spending cuts, based on 'fair taxation'.
Last updated Fri 16 Oct 2015 Politics Jersey
